    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained to a 'mint' standard. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original luster, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by authorized specialists. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
