    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin still retains its new-car scent; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun fading or imperfections. Every electronic component and convenience feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing on-time fluid changes and preventative maintenance. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and original alloy wheels that have never seen a curb. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule piece for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
